---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Start Here — Find Your Path into Tango — Tango Garden"
  description="New to tango? Curious but unsure? This page will help you take your first step into Argentine Tango in Cologne, calmly."
  canonical="https://tangogarden.de/pages/start-here"
>
  <Fragment set:html={`
<!-- HERO -->
<section id="start-hero" style="height: 100vh; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: url('/images/hero-dancers.webp') center/cover no-repeat;">
  <div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.2));"></div>
  <div style="position: relative; z-index: 2; text-align: center; width: 100%; max-width: 90%; padding: 0 20px; color: white;">
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(36px, 8vw, 56px); font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.2; color: white;">Start Here</h1>
    <p style="font-size: clamp(18px, 4.5vw, 24px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 30px;">New to tango? Curious but unsure?<br>This page will help you take your first step, calmly.</p>
    <a href="#three-ways-to-enter" style="display: inline-block; background: white; color: #2d5016; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; transition: all 0.3s ease; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);">Find your path ↓</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PATHWAY CARDS -->
<section id="three-ways-to-enter" style="background: white; padding: 20px 20px;">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 80px;">
      <div style="font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;">How to Start</div>
      <h2 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.2;">Three Ways to Enter the Garden</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 20px; color: #666; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;">Choose what feels right for where you are.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="garden-pathways-grid">

      <!-- Card 1: Enter the Garden -->
      <div class="pathway-card">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: -15px; right: -15px; width: 80px; height: 80px; background: rgba(45,80,22,0.08); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(45,80,22,0.15);">1</div>
        <div style="width: 70px; height: 70px; background: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 25px; font-size: 32px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">🌱</div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 26px; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 700;">Enter the Garden</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #666; margin-bottom: 25px;">One-time event for those who want to try without commitment.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 30px 0; text-align: left;">
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>One-time 1.5 hour session</li>
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>Connect with new people</li>
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>Drinks &amp; snacks included</li>
        </ul>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 12px; background: rgba(45,80,22,0.05); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
          <span>🗓️</span>
          <div style="text-align: left;">
            <span style="display: block; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">Next Event</span>
            <span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #4E5D22;">New dates coming soon (TBA)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top: 2px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1); flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
          <div style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;">
            <p class="card-price" style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 15px;">10€ or 8€ *</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/products/enter-the-garden-general-admission" style="display: block; background: white; color: #4E5D22; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 2px solid #4E5D22; transition: all 0.3s ease;">Start small →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Regular Classes (featured) -->
      <div class="pathway-card featured">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: -15px; right: -15px; width: 80px; height: 80px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">2</div>
        <div style="width: 70px; height: 70px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 25px; font-size: 32px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);">🌿</div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 26px; color: white; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 700;">Regular classes</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: 25px;">A steady weekly rhythm for optimal learning and growth.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 30px 0; text-align: left;">
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: white; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>10 weekly 1.5 hour sessions</li>
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: white; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>Community events &amp; Rituals</li>
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: white; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>Cover missed classes for free</li>
        </ul>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">
          <span>🗓️</span>
          <div style="text-align: left;">
            <span style="display: block; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 700;">Next Class (Course open until 31/03)</span>
            <span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: white;">No upcoming dates scheduled (TBA)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
          <div style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;">
            <p class="card-price" style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.1;">€13 or €10/class *</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/products/the-sprouting-sessions-beginner-level-full-course-pass-general-admission" style="display: block; background: white; color: #4E5D22; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); transition: all 0.3s ease; margin-bottom: 20px;">Commit to learning →</a>
          <a href="/collections" style="background: transparent; border: 2px solid white; color: white; padding: 10px 8px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; text-align: center;">or explore our flexible bundles</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Weekly Practicas -->
      <div class="pathway-card">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: -15px; right: -15px; width: 80px; height: 80px; background: rgba(45,80,22,0.08); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(45,80,22,0.15);">3</div>
        <div style="width: 70px; height: 70px; background: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 25px; font-size: 32px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">🌳</div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 26px; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 700;">Weekly Practicas</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #666; margin-bottom: 25px;">A relaxed space to practice, connect, and grow together.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 30px 0; text-align: left;">
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>Weekly 2.5 hour guided sessions</li>
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>Open-level and double-role</li>
          <li style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; position: relative;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>Community-focused atmosphere</li>
        </ul>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 12px; background: rgba(45,80,22,0.05); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
          <span>🗓️</span>
          <div style="text-align: left;">
            <span style="display: block; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 700;">Next Practica</span>
            <span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #4E5D22;">Wed, 22/07/2026<br>19:30 – 22:00</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top: 2px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1); flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
          <div style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;">
            <p class="card-price" style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 15px;">10€ or 8€ *</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/products/the-garden-practica-1-practica-pass-general-admission" style="display: block; background: white; color: #4E5D22; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 2px solid #4E5D22; transition: all 0.3s ease;">Accelerate your growth →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">* for students and anyone who is 28 years old or less</p>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50px 30px; background: #F9F7F2; border: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1); border-radius: 20px;">
      <h4 style="font-size: 22px; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Still wandering?</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 30px;">Every dancer starts somewhere different. If you're not sure where you fit, we're happy to guide you personally.</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/collections/all" class="safety-btn-info" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px 24px; color: #4E5D22; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; border-radius: 30px; background: rgba(45,80,22,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1); transition: all 0.2s ease;"><span style="margin-right: 8px;">📋</span> See all details</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/491602368723?text=Hi!%20I'm%20not%20sure%20which%20option%20is%20right%20for%20me..." class="safety-btn-primary" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px 24px; background: #4E5D22; color: white; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; border-radius: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45,80,22,0.2); transition: all 0.3s ease; border: 1px solid transparent;"><span style="margin-right: 8px;">💬</span> Chat on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- REASSURANCE -->
<section style="background: #F5F1E8; padding: 60px 0; width: 100%; margin: 0;">
  <div style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; text-align: center;">
    <h2 style="font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 38px); color: #2d5016; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.3;">If You're Unsure, You're Exactly Where You Should Be</h2>
    <p style="font-size: clamp(17px, 4vw, 20px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 30px;">Almost everyone who joins the garden starts with the same thoughts:</p>
    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.9; color: #555; text-align: left; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 30px;">
      <li style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1);">"I have no rhythm."</li>
      <li style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1);">"I don't know anyone."</li>
      <li style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1);">"I'm not a dancer."</li>
      <li style="padding: 10px 0;">"What if I feel awkward?"</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="font-size: clamp(18px, 4.2vw, 20px); line-height: 1.7; color: #2d5016; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 35px;">That's not a problem.<br>That's the starting point.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- IS THIS FOR YOU -->
<section id="is-this-for-you" style="background: white; padding: 60px 0; width: 100%; margin: 0;">
  <div style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
      <div style="font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #2d5016; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px;">Is This For You?</div>
      <h2 style="font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 42px); font-weight: bold; color: #2d5016; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.2;">This Space Is For You If</h2>
    </div>
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">
        <li style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;">✓</span>You're a young professional, student, or creative who misses real human connection</li>
        <li style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;">✓</span>You're comfortable in English, or want a space where language isn't a barrier</li>
        <li style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;">✓</span>You're curious about dance, but more curious about people</li>
        <li style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;">✓</span>You want to meet others without small talk, apps, or performance pressure</li>
        <li style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;">✓</span>You believe connection can be learned — and practiced</li>
      </ul>
      <div style="background: #F5F1E8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px 25px; text-align: center;">
        <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;">Here, we speak English first. But more importantly, we share a deeper language — touch, presence, and attention.</p>
        <p style="font-size: clamp(15px, 3.5vw, 16px); line-height: 1.6; color: #666; font-style: italic;">It may not be for you if you're looking for a drop-in workout with no community. And that's okay.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="common-questions" style="background: #F5F1E8; padding: 60px 0; width: 100%; margin: 0;">
  <div style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
      <div style="font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #2d5016; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px;">Common Questions</div>
      <h2 style="font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 42px); font-weight: bold; color: #2d5016; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.2;">Everything You're Wondering</h2>
      <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto;">No question is too small. Here are the ones we hear most.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">

      <div class="start-here-faq-item" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);">
        <button class="start-here-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" style="width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit;">
          Do I need any dance experience to start?
          <span class="start-here-faq-icon" style="flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="start-here-faq-answer">
          <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;">Not at all. Every session is designed for absolute beginners. We start from scratch — how to stand, how to be present, how to listen through touch. No prior dance experience is needed or expected.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="start-here-faq-item" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);">
        <button class="start-here-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" style="width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit;">
          Do I need to bring a partner?
          <span class="start-here-faq-icon" style="flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="start-here-faq-answer">
          <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;">No. Most people come alone. We rotate partners during class so everyone gets to dance with different people. In fact, coming solo often makes it easier to connect with the community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="start-here-faq-item" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);">
        <button class="start-here-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" style="width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit;">
          What should I wear?
          <span class="start-here-faq-icon" style="flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="start-here-faq-answer">
          <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;">Comfortable clothes you can move in. For shoes, we recommend either a clean pair of cozy socks, or a second pair of indoor shoes. Avoid thick rubber soles — they grip the floor and make turning difficult. We'll guide you on proper tango shoes once you decide to invest more.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="start-here-faq-item" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);">
        <button class="start-here-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" style="width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit;">
          Is the class taught in English?
          <span class="start-here-faq-icon" style="flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="start-here-faq-answer">
          <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;">Yes. All teaching is in English. Under request, we can also offer German, Russian and Greek. The deeper language of tango — presence, touch, listening — transcends words entirely.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="start-here-faq-item" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);">
        <button class="start-here-faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" style="width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit;">
          What's the difference between the three options?
          <span class="start-here-faq-icon" style="flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="start-here-faq-answer">
          <div style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
            <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Enter the Garden</strong> is a one-time introductory event — perfect if you want to get a feel for the space with zero commitment.</p>
            <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>Regular Classes</strong> are a full course that takes you from zero to dancing. This is the most effective path if you want to actually learn tango.</p>
